Package: libodb-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libodb0 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: library and header files to handle O files
 C++ library to read and write O format files files, binary or
 formatted. 
 .
 This package contains the headers and certain library files.

Package: libodb0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: shared library to handle O files
 C++ library to read and write O format files files, binary or
 formatted.
 .
 This package contains the shared library components needed for
 programs that have been compiled with the libodb library.
